window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Alex has truly made himself home in the fantasy world. With the help of his overpowered growth skill, his stats have soared higher and higher, reaching staggering heights. He's not the only one to benefit, as those wild gains also apply to the four lovely ladies at his side.<br> <br> With the Demon threat over, and Floternus saved, Alex can now focus his efforts on rebuilding the city, with perhaps a little bit of grinding here and there.<br> <br> At least, a long as nothing else pressing comes along...</p> <p>Authors note: Inspired by light novels, RPG's and mangas. Contains Isekai, light LitRPG/Gamelit stats, dungeons, magic, and a touch of trope.</p>"; 
